
units lj
dimension 3
atom_style molecular
angle_style hybrid harmonic
dihedral_style harmonic
bond_style fene
boundary p p p

neighbor 0.3 nsq
neigh_modify delay 5

read_data data.polymer2.lmp
read_data data.polymer2.lmp add append shift 0.0 5.0 0.0
read_data data.polymer2.lmp add append shift 0.0 -5.0 0.0
read_data data.polymer2.lmp add append shift 5.0 0.0 0.0
read_data data.polymer2.lmp add append shift -5.0 0.0 0.0
read_data data.polymer2.lmp add append shift -5.0 5.0 0.0
read_data data.polymer2.lmp add append shift -5.0 -5.0 0.0
read_data data.polymer2.lmp add append shift 5.0 5.0 0.0
read_data data.polymer2.lmp add append shift 5.0 -5.0 0.0


minimize 1.0e-4 1.0e-6 1000 10000

fix 1 all langevin 1.0 1.0 50.0 12345
fix 2 all nve

thermo 50
compute t all temp
compute ep all pe
compute ek all ke
compute ea all angle
compute tm all momentum


fix at1 all ave/time 1 5 5 c_t file temperatureDihedral.csv
fix at2 all ave/time 1 5 5 c_ep file potentialDihedral.csv
fix at3 all ave/time 1 5 5 c_ek file kineticDihedral.csv
fix at4 all ave/time 1 5 5 c_ea file angleDihedral.csv mode vector
fix at5 all ave/time 1 5 5 c_tm file momentumDihedral.csv mode vector

dump 1 all atom 50 dump.polymerDihedral

timestep 0.001
run 100000
